      </div>
 </div>
 
 
   <h2 class="title"><font color="#FB0034">Dreams do come true,you''ve got to go!</font></h2>
    
    <div class="review-rating">    
     
     <div class="rating-txt"><b>5 out of 5</b></div>
    </div>
   <div class="date">
    <b><span class="reviewed">Review Submitted: <span class="dtreviewed" title="2012-07-06">06 July 2012</span></span>
    <span class="stay">Date of Stay: <span class="dtreviewed">June 2012</span></span></b>
   </div>
   <div class="description review-txt"><b>
    What can we say, we were blown away! the views are amazing, not 
something you see every day! the pictures on the web are very good but 
you have got to see it to appreciate it. Accommodation was spot on 
everything you could possibly need,  well thought out, every utensil so 
you can cook if you want to. Several places to eat in Comares at very 
reasonable costs.
<br></b>  
<b><br>You couldn''t fault David and Jacquie,the owners, they were always 
there if you needed them and so friendly and welcoming,they certainly 
made the holiday for us!  Pool area was excellent and BBQ facility was 
very useful, covered area was wonderful shade for when it got too hot, 
with fridge where drinks and ice cream could be purchased for a very 
reasonable cost, again everything well thought out!
<br></b>
<b><br>What more can we say, perfect location, perfect accommodation, perfect hosts, we will definitely be going back!
<br></b>
<b><br>Paul (sicknote) &amp; Lauraine
