plate.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Pic/kinskygarden_eingangshalle.jpg" />          <!--[if !IE]>--> </object> <!--<![endif]--> </object></div><div class="cont" id="cb1"><div class="headline">Included services</div><font class="text"><div id="hotellogo" style="float:right; padding:2px;"><img src="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Img/342_Logo.png"></div><ul><li>2 nights for 2 persons in double room</li> <LI>extensive breakfast buffet included</LI>
<LI>free welcome drink</LI>
<LI>free highspeed wireless internet access</LI>
<LI>free to use internet-stations in the hotel</LI>
</ul></font><font class="text"><p>All above services are for 2 persons.</p></font></div><div class="bild" id="cb3"><img src="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Pic/kinskygarden_haus_abend.jpg" alt="BEST WESTERN Kinsky Garden****" \ > </div>
<div class="cont" id="cb4"><div class="headline">Welcome to BEST WESTERN Kinsky Garden</div><div class="text"><p><P>The luxury 4 star hotel&nbspBEST WESTERN&nbspKinsky Garden is overlooking homonymous gardens in a very attractive area of Prague - Mal&#225; Strana quarter. The location offers an ideal starting point for exploring the historical center of Prague. All main city attractions are within walking distance and public transportation facilities are located next to the hotel. The original historical building from 1890 was completely renovated in 1997 and the hotel offers quiet and unique atmosphere.<BR><BR>All 62 rooms have comfortable Italian furnishing, minibar, colour TV with satellite channels, air condition, direct telephone and private safe deposit box. Wi-fi internet connection is available in all guest rooms free of charge.</P></p></div></div>
<div id="cb5" class="bild"><object id="FlashID" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" height="310" width="700"> <param name="movie" value="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/ebay/static/swf.swf?xfile=342|Zimmer.xml"> <param name="quality" value="high"> <param   name="wmode" value="transparent"> <param   name="swfversion" value="6.0.65.0"> <!-- Dieses param-Tag fordert Benutzer von Flash Player 6.0 r65 und höher auf, die aktuelle Version von Flash Player herunterzuladen. Wenn Sie nicht wünschen, dass die Benutzer diese Aufforderung sehen, löschen Sie dieses Tag. --> <param name="expressinstall"   value="Scripts/expressInstall.swf"> <!-- Das nächste Objekt-Tag ist für Nicht-IE-Browser vorgesehen. Blenden Sie es daher mit IECC in IE aus. --> <!--[if !IE]>--> <object   type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/ebay/static/swf.swf?xfile=342|Zimmer.xml"   height="310" width="700">   <!--<![endif]--> <param name="quality"     value="high"> <param name="wmode"     value="transparent"> <param name="swfversion"     value="6.0.65.0"> <param     name="expressinstall"     value="Scripts/expressInstall.swf">   <!-- Im Browser wird für Benutzer von Flash Player 6.0 und älteren Versionen der folgende alternative Inhalt angezeigt. -->  <img src="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Pic/kinskygarden_zimmer2.jpg" />          <!--[if !IE]>--> </object> <!--<![endif]--> </object></div><div class="cont" id="cb6"><div class="headline">Hotel rooms</div><div class="text"><p><P>The hotel has 62 rooms in total, all are fully air-conditioned and there are special sound-proof windows. There are 8 single rooms, 48 double rooms and 6 double rooms with an extra bed. Bedding of single rooms is french bed, in double rooms queen size bed or two separate beds available.<BR><BR>All rooms have comfortable Italian furnishing, minibar, colour TV with satellite channels, air condition, direct telephone, hairdryer, additional inroom toiletries, desk/work space and private safe deposit box. All are with private bathroom - bath-tube or shower is available. Wi-fi internet connection is available in all rooms free of charge.<BR><BR>The windows of most of the rooms give upon the Kinsky garden. Some of the rooms are situated into the courtyard as well. Electronic door locking device is used for high security.</P></p></div></div>
<div class="bild" id="cb7"><img src="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Pic/kinskygarden_rezeption.jpg" alt="BEST WESTERN Kinsky Garden****" \ > </div>
<div class="cont" id="cb8"><div class="headline">The BEST WESTERN Kinsky Garden offers the following services</div><div class="text"><p>A 24-hour staffed reception with multilingual staff, room service, meeting facilities, foreign currency exchange, baby-sitting services on request, doctor on call, dry cleaning and laundry services. High speed wireless internet connection is provided in all guest rooms and public areas free of charge. Public computer is available for our clients. Consierge service is provided at the reception, ticket purchase to local events is offered. Cribs and rollaway beds, ironing boards and tea/coffee making facilities are available on request.</p></div></div>
<div id="cb9" class="bild"><object id="FlashID" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" height="310" width="700"> <param name="movie" value="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/ebay/static/swf.swf?xfile=342|Prag.xml"> <param name="quality" value="high"> <param   name="wmode" value="transparent"> <param   name="swfversion" value="6.0.65.0"> <!-- Dieses param-Tag fordert Benutzer von Flash Player 6.0 r65 und höher auf, die aktuelle Version von Flash Player herunterzuladen. Wenn Sie nicht wünschen, dass die Benutzer diese Aufforderung sehen, löschen Sie dieses Tag. --> <param name="expressinstall"   value="Scripts/expressInstall.swf"> <!-- Das nächste Objekt-Tag ist für Nicht-IE-Browser vorgesehen. Blenden Sie es daher mit IECC in IE aus. --> <!--[if !IE]>--> <object   type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/ebay/static/swf.swf?xfile=342|Prag.xml"   height="310" width="700">   <!--<![endif]--> <param name="quality"     value="high"> <param name="wmode"     value="transparent"> <param name="swfversion"     value="6.0.65.0"> <param     name="expressinstall"     value="Scripts/expressInstall.swf">   <!-- Im Browser wird für Benutzer von Flash Player 6.0 und älteren Versionen der folgende alternative Inhalt angezeigt. -->  <img src="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Pic/prag_prager_burg.jpg" />          <!--[if !IE]>--> </object> <!--<![endif]--> </object></div><div class="cont" id="cb10"><div class="headline">Prague, the Heart of Europe</div><div class="text"><p>Prague is the magical city of bridges, cathedrals, gold-tipped towers and church domes, whose image has been mirrored in the surface of the Vltava river for more than ten centuries. Prague is also a modern European metropolis full of energy, music, and art. <BR><BR>It&#39;s a city of contrasts: Serene green isles in the river and peaceful parks draping the city&#39;s seven hills are just steps away from the architectural treasures and bustling street life of the city center. Pragues&#39;s atmosphere is both intimate and romantic, and quite impossible to forget once you visit. <BR><BR>During a walk through the city, you will quickly discover that the history of European architecture has left behind splendid representatives of its various periods and styles. There are Romanesque, Gothic, Renaissance, Baroque, and Classicist buildings, as well as various neo-historic styles and Art Nouveau.</p></div></div>
<div class="bild" id="cb11"><img src="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/Hotel/342/Pic/kinskygarden_fruehstuecksraum.jpg" alt="BEST WESTERN Kinsky Garden****" \ > </div>
<div class="cont" id="kb"><div class="headline">Contact</div><table width="670" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td width="38%" valign="top" style="padding:2px;"><font class="text"><p>BEST WESTERN Kinsky Garden****<br>Holeckova 7<br>15000 Prag<br>Czech Republik<br>Tel: +420 2573 11173<br>Fax:+420 2573 11184<br>info@hotelkinskygarden.cz</p></font> </td><td valign="top" style="padding:2px;"><font class="text"><p>This voucher is valid one year from the purchase date. <br>Booking is subject to availability and is arranged directly with the hotel. <br><br>This voucher is not available on holidays, conference days and New Year&#39;s Eve.<br><br>Arrival is possible daily.</p></font></td></tr></table></div> </td></tr></table><br /><br /><center><object id="FlashID3" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" height="550" width="700"> <param name="movie" value="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/ebay/infobox/agbbox.swf?sprache=EN"> <param name="quality" value="high"> <param name="wmode" value="transparent"> <param name="swfversion" value="6.0.65.0"> <!-- Dieses param-Tag fordert Benutzer von Flash Player 6.0 r65 und höher auf, die aktuelle Version von Flash Player herunterzuladen. Wenn Sie nicht wünschen, dass die Benutzer diese Aufforderung sehen, löschen Sie dieses Tag. --> <param name="expressinstall" value="Scripts/expressInstall.swf"> <!-- Das nächste Objekt-Tag ist für Nicht-IE-Browser vorgesehen. Blenden Sie es daher mit IECC in IE aus. --> <!--[if !IE]>--> <object type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://template.touristik-vertrieb.at/ebay/infobox/agbbox.swf?sprache=EN" height="550" width="700"> <!--<![endif]--> <param name="quality" value="high"> <param name="wmode" value="transparent"> <param name="swfversion" value="6.0.65.0"> <param name="expressinstall" value="Scripts/expressInstall.swf"> <!-- Im Browser wird für Benutzer von Flash Player 6.0 und älteren Versionen der folgende alternative Inhalt angezeigt. --> <div> <h4>F&uuml;r den Inhalt dieser Seite ist eine neuere Version von Adobe Flash Player erforderlich.</h4> <p><a href="http://www.adobe.com/go/getflashplayer"><img src="http://www.adobe.com/images/shared/download_buttons/get_flash_player.gif" alt="Adobe Flash Player herunterladen" height="33" width="112"></a></p> </div> <!--[if !IE]>--> </object> <!--<![endif]--> </object></center></td></tr></table></body><p style="display:none;">englllishhh</p> <p style="display:none;">Sie legen viel Wert auf Qualität, Komfort und guten Service? Sie möchten bei Ihrer Hotelbuchung flexibel bleiben? Sie buchen Städtetrips und Kurzreisen genauso gerne wie Strandurlaub, Wintersportreisen und andere längere Aufenthalte? Auch mit Gutscheinversicherung möglich. Jetzt günstige Hotels weltweit buchen. Eine große Auswahl an Hotels, Unterkünften, Resorts, Ferienhotels, Sporthotels sowie Stadthotels. Ob Oberösterreich, Salzburg, Steiermark oder Tirol, ganz egal auch Italien, Spanien, Frankreich oder sogar weltweit. Beliebte Desitanationen wie Griechenland oder der Garda See. Oder einfach Wellness Urlaub vom feinsten.</p></html>')
