<p style="font-family: verdana;"><strong><font face="verdana"><font face="Verdana">To view the apartments and for further details please go to our website,&nbsp;unfortunately eBay will not allow me to publish this on either the auction or on my about me page, please&nbsp;contact me&nbsp;for this address.&nbsp; Our email address is <a href="mailto:bookings@guyscliffe.co.uk">guyscliffe@trish.fsbusiness.co.uk</a>&nbsp;and my&nbsp;business seller details are listed at the end of this auction.&nbsp;</font></font></strong></p>
