<p style="font-family: verdana;"><strong><font face="arial">Centrally situated in&nbsp;the heart of&nbsp;the English Riviera&nbsp;- at Preston Sands, Paignton - 1 mile Torquay and approx 5 miles Brixham/Dartmouth/Totnes/Newton Abbot.&nbsp;&nbsp;Take advantage of our milder climate and get away for a few days.&nbsp; Own car park and garden on premises.&nbsp; </font><font face="arial">Friendly family&nbsp;owned and run&nbsp;accommodation - we are members of the FSB (Federation of Small Businesses).</font></strong></p>
