<p align="left" style="font-family: verdana;"><font face="arial"><strong>Wind/kite surfing (all year round), Paignton Zoo and Botanical Gardens, Living Coasts, Babbacombe Model Village,&nbsp;Kents&nbsp;Caverns,&nbsp;South Devon Steam Railway to Kingswear/Dartmouth, fishing/boat trips, and of course fresh Brixham fish and Devon Cream Teas!&nbsp; (Just a small selection of some of the things to do)&nbsp; Also, ideal location for walking the&nbsp;South West Coastal Path&nbsp;or Dartmoor, or convenient for touring both Devon and Cornwall, lots to do whatever the weather!</strong></font></p>
