make the whole process smooth and stress free, something we aim for in 
all the rentals we look after.&nbsp;<br>Thank you very much once again</div><div class="review-bottom" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px;"><div class="review-rating" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left;"><div class="rating-txt" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; float: left; font-size: 0.7979em;">Rating 5 out of 5</div></div><br></div></div></div><div id="hreview-ffbffeba-882a-a1b2-b87f-24610f4a540a" class="hreview review-box last" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 230, 243); position: relative; min-height: 180px;" lang="en"><div class="review-reviewer" style="margin: 0px 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; width: 140px; min-height: 1em; float: left;"><br></div><div class="review-content" style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 521.0333251953125px; font-size: 0.9393em;"><h2 class="title summary" style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.238em; clear: both; font-size: 1.2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Excellent apartment in great location.</h2><div class="date" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span class="reviewed" style="padding-right: 15px;">Review Submitted:&nbsp;<span class="dtreviewed" title="2011-02-08" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">08 February 2011</span></span>&nbsp;<span class="stay">Date of Stay:&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">October 2010</span></span></div><div class="description review-txt" style="margin: 0.7em 0px 0px; padding: 0px;">This
