hiccups but these were swiftly &amp; unobtrusively taken care of by the 
ultra efficient Debbie who, as the previous reviewer points out, is also
 a wealth of helpful local information.&nbsp;<br><br>We will be passing on 
our highest recommendations for this apartment, its location and the 
helpful service offered by everyone involved to our family and friends 
and we will certainly be looking to return.&nbsp;<br><br>Hasta Pronto Espero!</div><div class="review-response" style="margin: 0.7em 0px 10px; padding: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 244); border: 1px dashed rgb(204, 204, 204); text-align: justify;"><b>Owner''s Response:&nbsp;</b>What
